  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education &amp; nutrition for 60 children in Peru</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We aim to provide better primary education to 60 children in Maldonaldo, Arequipa, in Peru who currently only have one national teacher. By employing more local teachers and providing materials we can give the children a much better education.    Due to COVID-19 we aim to provide hand sanitizer and supplies of soap over the long-term for all our students for when they enter and leave the school each day to reassure parents that it is a safe environment.</narrative>
  </description>
